- Set in Australia (any city)
- A realistic SME (15-60 employees, $2M-$50M revenue)
- With a scenario that has genuine tension and no easy answer
- With 5-7 employees who have distinct personalities and sometimes disagree
- With specific, realistic details (dollar amounts, percentages, dates, vendor names)

Be creative with the company concept — don't just make a generic version of the industry. Give it character, a founding story, and a specific market position.

